txt.en: While searching for relics of the Rohirrim at Atburg, you found a relic of Dunlending-make recovered by the brigands from the Field of Celebrant.
This relic is clearly of Dunlending-make, not of the Rohirrim. Perhaps it may still be of interest to someone at Aculf's camp in the Rushgore.
There are Rohirrim at Aculf's camp in the Rushgore, north-west of Atburg.\n\nYou should bring the Dunlending relic to one of the Rohirrim.
'What? Why should I care...?\n\n'Wait...I have an idea, but I will require more of these relics. Return to Atburg and seek more, [placeholder].'
Dunlending relics might be found on brigands at Atburg, south-east of Aculf's camp in the Rushgore.\n\nBagmund wants you to find more Dunlending relics for him.
Bagmund is at Aculf's camp in the Rushgore, north-west of Atburg.\n\nYou should bring the Dunlending relics to Bagmund at once.
'Ha! Aye, these will do...they will do just fine!'
'I need more of these relics, [placeholder]...do not let me down!'
Talk to someone at Aculf's camp in the Rushgore
Bring the Dunlending relics to Bagmund at Aculf's camp in the Rushgore
